request.description:
Get current balance of multiple wallets, up to 20 wallets.

Returns: Current balance (in minimum denom) of each wallet. Plus "erc20" field is token balance for mapped erc20/ibc pairs

Sample response:

``` json
{
    "status": "1",
    "message": "OK",
    "result": [
        {
            "account": "0x111...", // evm-style address of wallet
            "cosmosAccount": "evmos1aaa...", // cosmos-style address of wallet
            "balance": "1000", // coin balance
            "erc20": "2000", // ERC20 balance, only visible when API key is Pro
        },
        {
            "account": "0x222...", // evm-style address of wallet
            "cosmosAccount": "evmos1bbb...", // cosmos-style address of wallet
            "balance": "500", // coin balance
            "erc20": "600", // ERC20 balance, only visible when API key is Pro
        },
    ],
    "contract": "0x...", // ERC20 smart contract (1-1 mapped with IBC denom) or empty if ibc denom not mapped, only visible when API key is Pro
    // "notice": "Upgrade API Pro to get ERC20 balance" // This field only visible if your API key is not Pro
}

```

Get top holders (100) of specific coin.

Data refresh per every 12 hours

Sample response:

``` json
{
    "status": "1",
    "message": "OK",
    "result": [
        {
            "tokenHolderAddress": "0x...",
            "tokenHolderCosmosAddress": "{{bech32-prefix}}1aaa...",
            "tokenHolderQuantity": 121492984 // minimum denom
        },
        {
            "tokenHolderAddress": "0x...",
            "tokenHolderCosmosAddress": "{{bech32-prefix}}1bbb...",
            "tokenHolderQuantity": 59768003 // minimum denom
        },
    ]
}

```

Get daily price of coinbase in specified date range, upto 90 days.

Require API Pro.

Sample response:

``` json
{
    "status": "1",
    "message": "OK",
    "result": [
        {
            "utcDate": "2023-01-06",
            "unixTimeStamp": "1672963200",
            "value": "0.460798" // USD
        },
        {
            "utcDate": "2023-01-07",
            "unixTimeStamp": "1673049600",
            "value": "0.451491" // USD
        },
    ]
}

```
